--- FOUNDATION [THE CATALOG'S VAULT] (ARCHIVED) ---

TRUE PRICE:
  Material: 85,000¥ (safe), KT-77f Regulator, "Zero-Point" Lock Suite, "Shroud" Cloak.
  Informational: Encrypted server with client lists (Charter, WYRM-SIGN), "Project Sunspot" packet.
  Narrative: "The Man Who Knew the Echo." Arrogant archivist of the weird.

KEY CHALLENGE:
  Security: Service panel, Rating 5 maglock + vibration sensor. Crawlspace pressure plates (3-7-1-5-2) disable Rating 4 laser grid. Overwatch team (Aegis, 4 members).

Status: [ARCHIVED / RESOLVED]

